'''2015年11月巴黎襲擊案'''（{{lang-fr|Attentats du 13 novembre 2015 en Île-de-France}}）是2015年11月13日與14日凌晨發生於[[法國|法國]][[巴黎|巴黎]]及其北郊[[聖但尼_(塞納-聖但尼省)|圣但尼]]的連續[[恐怖袭擊|恐怖袭擊]]事件。袭击事件共造成來自26個國家的127人當場遇难<ref name="RTE 20">{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2015/1120/747897-paris/|title=Paris attacks death toll rises to 130|publisher=RTE News|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121143854/http://www.rte.ie/news/2015/1120/747897-paris/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，3人到院後不治身亡，80-99人重伤<ref name="Telegraph-11995246">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995246/Paris-shooting-What-we-know-so-far-on-Wednesday-afternoon.html|title=Paris attacks: Everything we know on Wednesday evening|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2015-11-18|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119081020/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995246/Paris-shooting-What-we-know-so-far-on-Wednesday-afternoon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，368人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/injuries-from-paris-attacks-will-take-long-to-heal/|title=Injuries from Paris attacks will take long to heal|publisher=CBS|author=M. Marcus|date=2015-11-19|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120185024/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/injuries-from-paris-attacks-will-take-long-to-heal/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC-34836330">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34836330|title=Search goes on for missing|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-11-16|accessdate=2015-11-17|archive-date=2019-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405072350/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34836330|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中[[巴塔克蘭劇院|巴塔克兰剧院]]的观众被恐怖分子挟持为人质，造成89人死亡<ref name="F24-20151115">{{cite news|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20151115-paris-attacks-bataclan-what-we-know-attacker-victims-arrests-belgium|title=Paris attacks: What we know so far|publisher=France 24|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-17|archive-date=2019-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208204842/https://www.france24.com/en/20151115-paris-attacks-bataclan-what-we-know-attacker-victims-arrests-belgium|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外案發當時有7名袭击者拒捕並以炸彈自殺，法国政府隨後继续開展追查帮凶的行動<ref name="GuardNov15_2">{{cite news|author=Claire Phipps|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-15|title=Paris attacker named as Ismaïl Omar Mostefai as investigation continues – live updates|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/15/paris-attacker-named-investigation-continues-live-updates|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515060240/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/15/paris-attacker-named-investigation-continues-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

袭击事件始于[[欧洲中部时间|欧洲中部时间]]11月13日21时20分，3名自杀式炸弹袭击者袭击了位于圣但尼的法兰西体育场附近，随后巴黎的咖啡馆、餐馆及音乐场所发生自杀式炸弹袭击和大规模枪击<ref name="reuterstimeline"/>。恐怖組織[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]（IS）宣布对此事件负责<ref name="ISIS">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/11/14/world/paris-attacks/|title=ISIS claims responsibility of Paris attacks|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2015-11-14|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507075910/https://www.cnn.com/2015/11/14/world/paris-attacks/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/fr/urgent/20151114-lorganisation-etat-islamique-revendique-attentats-paris|title=L'organisation État islamique revendique les attentats de Paris|date=2015-11-14|publisher=France 24|language=fr|accessdate=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114163337/http://www.france24.com/fr/urgent/20151114-lorganisation-etat-islamique-revendique-attentats-paris|archive-date=2015-11-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，并称这是为了报复法国在[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]对IS目标的空袭<ref name=Guardian1>{{cite news|last1=Elgot|first1=Jessica|last2=Phipps|first2=Claire|last3=Bucks|first3=Jonathan|date=2015-11-14|title=Paris attacks: Islamic State says killings were response to Syria strikes|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/14/paris-terror-attacks-attackers-dead-mass-killing-live-updates|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-11-14|quote=The group says the killings were in response to airstrikes against its militants in Syria, adding France would remain a "key target".|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503231150/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/14/paris-terror-attacks-attackers-dead-mass-killing-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Dalton|first1=Matthew|last2=Varela|first2=Thomas|last3=Landauro|first3=Inti|title=Paris Attacks Were an 'Act of War' by Islamic State, French President François Hollande Says|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/paris-attacks-were-an-act-of-war-by-islamic-state-french-president-francois-hollande-says-1447498080|website=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2015-11-14|date=2015-11-14|quote=Islamic State claimed responsibility for the attacks on a social media account, but didn't provide specific information that would allow the claim to be verified. It said the attacks were retaliation for French airstrikes against the group in Syria and Iraq.|archive-date=2017-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801221108/http://www.wsj.com/articles/paris-attacks-were-an-act-of-war-by-islamic-state-french-president-francois-hollande-says-1447498080|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法国时任总统[[弗朗索瓦·奥朗德|弗朗索瓦·奥朗德]]称这次袭击是IS组织策划于[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]、组织于[[比利时|比利时]]并与其法国同谋实施的战争行为<ref>{{cite web|title=Paris attacks: Hollande blames Islamic State for 'act of war'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34820016|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2015-11-14|date=2014-11-14|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226110149/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34820016|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT act of war">{{cite news|last1=Nossiter|first1=Adam|last2=Breeden|first2=Aurelien|last3=Bennhold|first3=Katrin|title=Three Teams of Coordinated Attackers Carried Out Assault on Paris, Officials Say; Hollande Blames ISIS|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/15/world/europe/paris-terrorist-attacks.html|accessdate=2015-11-14|work=The New York Times|date=2015-11-14|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524005410/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/15/world/europe/paris-terrorist-attacks.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thomsonreutersfoundation">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/14/us-france-shooting-hollande-idUSKCN0T30JG20151114|title=Hollande says Paris attacks 'an act of war' by Islamic State|publisher=Thomson Reuters Foundation|accessdate=2015-11-14|date=2015-11-14|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114214350/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/14/us-france-shooting-hollande-idUSKCN0T30JG20151114|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="CoordinatedAttacks">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/11/15/world/europe/manhunt-for-paris-attackers.html|title=Finding the Links Among the Paris Attackers|author=Alicia Parlapiano, Wilson Andrews, Haeyoun Park and Larry Buchanan|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2015-11-17|accessdate=2015-11-17|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116214422/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/11/15/world/europe/manhunt-for-paris-attackers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

为应对恐怖袭击，奥朗德宣布法国全国进入紧急状态<ref name="NYT act of war" />，并实施临时边境管控<ref name="GuardNov15" />。11月15日，法国对叙利亚境内的伊斯兰国据点[[拉卡|拉卡]]发动空袭，此为[[夏馬風行動|夏马风行动]]史上最大的一次行动<ref name=rubin>{{cite news|last1=Rubin|first1=Alissa|title=France Strikes ISIS Targets in Syria in Retaliation for Attacks|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/16/world/europe/paris-terror-attack.html|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-date=2019-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523165756/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/16/world/europe/paris-terror-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月18日，恐怖袭击主谋[[阿卜杜勒-哈米德·阿巴乌德|阿卜杜勒-哈米德·阿巴乌德]]与其他至少两名嫌犯在警方的圣但尼突袭中死亡<ref name="chief suspect">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/19/world/europe/paris-attacks.html|title=Chief Suspect in Paris Attacks Died in Raid, France Says|author=Aurelien Breeden, Kimiko de Freytas-Tamura|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2015-11-19|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502165201/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/19/world/europe/paris-attacks.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

继2015年1月造成17人死亡的{{le|2015年1月法兰西岛袭击案|January 2015 Île-de-France attacks|法兰西岛袭击事件}}后，法国一直处于高度戒备状态<ref name="AFP summary" />。11月的袭击是法国自[[二战|二战]]以来最严重的恐怖袭击事件<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/14/paris-attacks-people-throw-open-doors-to-help|title=Parisians throw open doors in wake of attacks, but Muslims fear repercussions|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2015-11-14|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119045510/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/14/paris-attacks-people-throw-open-doors-to-help|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/paris-terror-attacks/paris-terror-attacks-yes-parisians-are-traumatised-but-the-spirit-of-resistance-still-lingers-34201891.html|title=Yes, Parisians are traumatised, but the spirit of resistance still lingers|first=Nafeesa|last=Syeed|newspaper=The Irish Independent|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120093545/http://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/paris-terror-attacks/paris-terror-attacks-yes-parisians-are-traumatised-but-the-spirit-of-resistance-still-lingers-34201891.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是欧盟自2004年[[馬德里三一一連環爆炸案|马德里三一一连环爆炸案]]以来最严重的恐怖袭击事件<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/europe/europe-s-open-border-policy-may-become-latest-victim-of-terrorism-1.2435486|title=Europe's open-border policy may become latest victim of terrorism|newspaper=The Irish Times|date=2015-11-19|accessdate=2015-11-19|archive-date=2019-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190322235013/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/europe/europe-s-open-border-policy-may-become-latest-victim-of-terrorism-1.2435486|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年6月29日，法國[[巴黎司法宮|巴黎司法宮]]特別法庭針對2015年參與者做出判決，20名被告均被判有罪<ref>{{Cite web |title=「世紀審判」落幕 巴黎恐攻唯一倖存主謀遭判終身監禁 {{!}} 國際 {{!}} CTWANT |url=https://www.ctwant.com/article/192163 |website=www.ctwant.com |language=zh-TW |access-date=2022-06-30}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
2014年9月14日，法国开始介入[[叙利亚內戰|叙利亚內戰]]，并发起了一系列军事行动，其中知名的有[[夏马风行动|夏马风行动]]。此外，法國也參與美國為首對恐怖組織[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的空襲行動。2015年10月法国第一次成为叙利亚圣战者的打击目标<ref>{{cite web |script-title=en:Middle east – 'Terrorists have no passports,’ French PM says of Syria air strikes |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20151012-france-pm-valls-terrorists-have-no-passports-air-strikes-french-jihadists-syria |website=France 24 |publisher=Google |accessdate=2015-11-14 |language=en |archive-date=2017-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622221140/http://www.france24.com/en/20151012-france-pm-valls-terrorists-have-no-passports-air-strikes-french-jihadists-syria |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年11月，法国更宣佈將部署[[戴高樂號航空母艦|戴高樂號航空母艦]]打擊伊斯蘭國<ref>{{cite news|author1=路西|title=法國將部署航空母艦打擊「伊斯蘭國」|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/11/151105_france_carrier_mideast|publisher=BBC|date=2015-11-05|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116233918/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/11/151105_france_carrier_mideast|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

巴黎曾于2015年1月7日發生由激進派穆斯林發動的[[查理周刊总部枪击案|查理周刊总部枪击案]]，造成12死11伤，該槍擊案案發地正位于此次主要案發地之一的[[巴黎十一區|巴黎第11區]]。彼時[[法兰西岛|法兰西岛]]和[[皮卡第|皮卡第]]的威胁级别曾提升至{{link-en|最高戒备状态|Vigipirate}}。此外在2015年2月還曾發生對猶太中心的襲擊<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31118020|title = French soldiers wounded in Nice Jewish centre attack|last = |first = |date = 2015-02-03|work = [[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118183533/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31118020|dead-url = no}}</ref>，2015年6月在[[里昂|里昂]]附近的[[聖屈昂坦法拉維耶恐怖攻擊事件|砍頭事件]]，以及2015年8月的[[大力士高速列車槍擊案|大力士高速列車槍擊案]]。在此次襲擊一周前，法國為應對即將在11月末至12月初舉行的[[2015年聯合國氣候變化大會|2015年聯合國氣候變化大會]]加强安保措施，如恢復邊境檢查<ref>{{Cite news |url = http://www.webcitation.org/6d1kwppjd |title = Gunmen kill more than 120 in wave of attacks across Paris |authors = Randolph, Eric and Simon Valmary |date = 2015-11-13 |work = [[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]], [[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] |accessdate = 2015-11-14 |archive-date = 2016-03-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160328213639/http://www.webcitation.org/6d1kwppjd |dead-url = no }}</ref>。10月底，一架俄國自埃及出發的客機遭到炸毀。土耳其、伊拉克和以色列的情報機構在襲擊前曾警告法國本土將遭到襲擊，但法國當局并未作出回應<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://news.antiwar.com/2015/11/15/french-jews-warned-friday-morning-of-impending-large-terrorist-attack/|script-title = en:French Jews Warned Friday Morning of ‘Impending Large Terrorist Attack’ Netanyahu: Israel Passed Intelligence to France on Attack|last = Ditz|first = Jason|date = 2015-11-15|work = antiwar.com|accessdate = |language = en|archive-date = 2015-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117160428/http://news.antiwar.com/2015/11/15/french-jews-warned-friday-morning-of-impending-large-terrorist-attack/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

此次巴黎恐怖襲擊發生于[[伊斯蘭曆|伊斯蘭曆]][[色法尔月|色法爾月]]的第一天。伊斯蘭國曾將其比喻作“غزوة”（[[加齊|Ghazwa]]）<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/religion/4-ways-isis-grounds-its-actions-in-religion-and-why-it-should-matter-commentary/2015/11/16/d7e31278-8ca0-11e5-934c-a369c80822c2_story.html|title = 4 ways ISIS grounds its actions in religion, and why it should matter (COMMENTARY)|last = Ibrahim|first = Ayman S.|date = 2015-11-16|work = |accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118061536/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/religion/4-ways-isis-grounds-its-actions-in-religion-and-why-it-should-matter-commentary/2015/11/16/d7e31278-8ca0-11e5-934c-a369c80822c2_story.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，意為“打擊異教徒的義舉”，以削弱和瓦解異教徒的攻擊，并最終征服和奴役敵人<ref>{{Cite book|title = Cambridge History of Islam|last = |first = |publisher = |year = |isbn = |location = |pages = p. 269}}</ref>。

