==== 畢查街和阿里伯特街 ====
第一宗槍擊約 21:20 發生于畢查街和阿里伯特街交界、臨近[[圣马丁运河|聖馬丁運河]]的區域。槍手首先向阿里伯特街著名酒吧“乐钟琴”（Le Carillon）外的人群射擊<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/11/13/multiple-deaths-reported-after-shootings-explosions-paris/75727746/|title = Scores killed in Paris terror attacks at six separate sites|last = Doug|first = Stanglin|date = 2015-11-13|work = USA Today|accessdate = |archive-date = 2017-07-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170722150301/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/11/13/multiple-deaths-reported-after-shootings-explosions-paris/75727746/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，然後轉向畢查街，向餐館“小柬埔寨”（Le Petit Cambodge）裏的人開槍<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.storm.mg/article/73824|title = 巴黎恐攻》至少129人罹難 法國近代史上最嚴重 全國進入緊急狀態|last = 李佳恒，閻紀宇，李忠謙|first = |date = 2015-11-14|work = 風傳媒|accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114073228/http://www.storm.mg/article/73824|dead-url = no}}</ref>，隨後駕駛一兩輛車逃離<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/November_2015_Paris_attacks#cite_note-National_Post_2015-1-72|title = 'It's a horror': Hollande orders French borders closed after Paris terror attack leaves at least 149 dead|last = |first = |date = National Post|work = 13 November 2015|accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151119183744/https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/November_2015_Paris_attacks#cite_note-National_Post_2015-1-72|dead-url = no}}</ref>，其中至少一輛爲比利時車牌<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = http://www.lemonde.fr/attaques-a-paris/article/2015/11/14/rue-bichat-on-ecoutait-de-la-musique-quand-on-a-entendu-ce-qu-on-pensait-etre-des-petards_4809562_4809495.html|script-title = fr:Attaques à Paris : « On pensait que c’étaient des pétards. C’étaient des scènes de guerre »|last = Editors|first = |date = 2015-11-14|work = Le Monde|accessdate = |language = fr|archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114060957/http://www.lemonde.fr/attaques-a-paris/article/2015/11/14/rue-bichat-on-ecoutait-de-la-musique-quand-on-a-entendu-ce-qu-on-pensait-etre-des-petards_4809562_4809495.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。警方表示此次襲擊造成11人死亡<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url = http://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/13/shootings-reported-in-eastern-paris-live|title = Paris attacks kill more than 120 people – as it happened|last = Kevin|first = Rawlinson|date = 2015-11-13|work = the Guardian|accessdate = |archive-date = 2020-04-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200426144053/https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2015%2Fnov%2F13%2Fshootings-reported-in-eastern-paris-live|dead-url = no}}</ref>。有目擊者聽見槍手大喊“真主至大”。有旁近聖路易斯醫院（Hôpital Saint-Louis）的醫護人員當時正在“乐钟琴”酒吧内，在襲擊后立即對傷者采取了救護措施<ref name=":0" />。

==== 國王噴泉街 ====
一名襲擊者于 21:32 手持機槍在位于畢查街以南國王噴泉街的 Café Bonne Bière 外、接近意大利餐館 La Casa Nostra 的地方開槍<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/2015/11/14/01016-20151114ARTFIG00228-attentats-de-paris-le-point-sur-l-enquete-24-heures-apres-les-faits.php|title = Attentats de Paris : le point sur l'enquête 24 heures après les faits|last = |first = |date = 2015-11-14|work = Le Figaro|accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114230804/http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/2015/11/14/01016-20151114ARTFIG00228-attentats-de-paris-le-point-sur-l-enquete-24-heures-apres-les-faits.php|dead-url = no}}</ref>。巴黎檢察官稱有5人喪生，8人受傷<ref name=":1" />。

==== 夏洪街 ====
兩名襲擊者于約 21:36 向夏洪街的酒吧餐廳 La Belle Équipe 射擊數分鐘，隨後駕車逃離<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34814203|title = Paris attacks: Bataclan and other assaults leave many dead|last = |first = |date = 2015-11-14|work = BBC|accessdate = |archive-date = 2019-09-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190912043521/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34814203|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34818994|title = Paris attacks: What happened on the night|last = |first = |date = 2015-11-16|work = BBC News|accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-11-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151119103015/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34818994|dead-url = no}}</ref>，并造成19人死亡、9人危殆<ref name=":2" />。

==== 伏爾泰大道 ====
約 21:40 時，一名襲擊者在[[伏尔泰大道|伏爾泰大道]]接近[[民族广场_(巴黎)|民族廣場]]（place de la Nation）的Comptoir Voltaire餐館引爆身上所携帶的炸彈身亡，造成16人受傷，其中一人重傷<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/fait-divers/a-nation-le-kamikaze-s-est-fait-sauter-en-passant-la-commande_1735885.html|title = A Nation, le kamikaze s'est fait sauter en passant la commande|authors = Randolph, Eric and Simon Valmary|date = 2015-11-13|work = lexpress.fr|accessdate = 2015-11-14|archive-date = 2015-11-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151119060508/http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/fait-divers/a-nation-le-kamikaze-s-est-fait-sauter-en-passant-la-commande_1735885.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。
