=== 巴塔克蘭劇院劫持與大規模射殺事件 ===
[[巴塔克蘭劇院|巴塔克蘭劇院]]當晚也發生了槍擊與劫持事件。當時來自美國加州的搖滾樂團“死亡金屬之鷹”（Eagles of Death Metal）正在該地演出，場下約有1,500名觀眾<ref name=GuardNov15>{{cite news |last1=Rawlinson |first1=Kevin |title=Fatal shootings and explosion reported in Paris – live |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/13/shootings-reported-in-eastern-paris-live |accessdate=2015-11-13 |work=The Guardian |date=2015-11-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113215624/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/nov/13/shootings-reported-in-eastern-paris-live |archivedate=2015-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Nossiter 2015">{{cite web|last = Nossiter|first = Adam|title = Multiple Attacks Roil Paris; President Hollande Is Evacuated From Stadium|website = The New York Times|date = 2015-11-13|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/14/world/europe/multiple-attacks-roil-paris-president-hollande-is-evacuated-from-stadium.html|accessdate = 2015-11-13|archive-date = 2015-11-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151113215650/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/14/world/europe/multiple-attacks-roil-paris-president-hollande-is-evacuated-from-stadium.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。演唱會大約進行了一小時後，四名配有[[AK-47突擊步槍|AK-47突擊步槍]]的黑衣男子衝入會場<ref name="AFP summary" />。目擊者聽見一名槍手用[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]大喊「真主至大」，接著便有條不紊地朝著群眾開火<ref name=Nossiter>{{cite news|last1=Nossiter|first1=Adam|last2=Higgins|first2=Andrew|script-title=en:‘Scene of Carnage’ Inside Sold-Out Paris Concert Hall|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/14/world/europe/paris-attacks.html|accessdate=2015-11-14|agency=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2015-11-13|language=en|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114091210/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/14/world/europe/paris-attacks.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AFP summary">{{cite web | url=http://news.yahoo.com/least-120-dead-paris-attacks-investigation-source-pta-013205822.html;_ylt=AwrC1DFcskZWYBkAKh_QtDMD;_ylu=X3oDMTByOHZyb21tBGNvbG8DYmYxBHBvcwMxBHZ0aWQDBHNlYwNzcg-- | title=More than 120 people killed in Paris 'terror' attacks | publisher=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] | work=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] | date=2015-11-13 | accessdate=2015-11-14 | author=Randolph, Eric and Simon Valmary | archive-date=2015-11-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114202028/http://news.yahoo.com/least-120-dead-paris-attacks-investigation-source-pta-013205822.html;_ylt=AwrC1DFcskZWYBkAKh_QtDMD;_ylu=X3oDMTByOHZyb21tBGNvbG8DYmYxBHBvcwMxBHZ0aWQDBHNlYwNzcg-- | dead-url=no }}</ref>。一名目擊者表示，他看見一位武裝男子進入巴塔克蘭劇院，並有二或三位未蒙面男子向群眾掃射<ref name="BBCNewsLive" />。這起攻擊事件持續了約20分鐘，更有目擊者表示，攻擊者向人群丟擲[[手榴彈|手榴彈]]<ref name=Nossiter/>。曾參與這場演唱會的電台記者朱利安·皮爾斯（{{lang|en|Julien Pearce}}）向[[CNN|CNN]]描述，這些恐怖分子相當冷靜且堅決，並重新填裝了三至四次彈藥<ref name=Nossiter/>。

大約在晚上十點左右，警方在劇院外部署行動，該名男子開始挾持人質<ref name=Nossiter/>。約有60至100名人質被挾持<ref name="Goldstein 2015">{{cite web |last=Goldstein |first=Sasha |title=At least 26 dead after explosion, shooting reported in Paris |website=NY Daily News |date=2015-11-13 |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/dead-explosions-shooting-reported-paris-article-1.2434381 |accessdate=2015-11-13 |archive-date=2017-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808090253/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/dead-explosions-shooting-reported-paris-article-1.2434381 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GuardNov15" />。而樂團成員則毫髮無傷地順利離開<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abc7.com/news/singer-for-eagles-of-death-metal-escapes-paris-attack/1083890/|title=Singer for Eagles of Death Metal escapes Paris attack|work=abc7.com|location=Los Angeles|accessdate=2015-11-13|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114123152/http://abc7.com/news/singer-for-eagles-of-death-metal-escapes-paris-attack/1083890/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。BBC引述目擊者表示，當時約有60位民眾倉皇逃出劇院，躲進附近的民宅裡。一名逃出的目擊者告訴記者說，恐怖分子大概有五至六名，且他們提到了[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞]]<ref name="BBCNewsLive" /><ref>{{cite web|first=Adam|last=Nossiter|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/paris-attacks-live-updates/survivors-of-hostage-siege-taken-to-hospitals-or-police-station/|title=Survivors of Hostage Siege Taken to Hospitals or Police Station|work=The New York Times|date=2015-11-13|accessdate=2015-11-13|location=Paris, France|quote=one of them shouted, “What you are doing in Syria, you are going to pay for it now!”|language=en|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025012/http://www.nytimes.com/live/paris-attacks-live-updates/survivors-of-hostage-siege-taken-to-hospitals-or-police-station/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一位在巴塔克蘭劇院裡的目擊者說道槍手曾大喊「這一切起因於法國總統[[奧朗德|奧朗德]]在世界各地對穆斯林的迫害」<ref>{{cite web|last=Higgins|first=Andrew|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/paris-attacks-live-updates/this-is-because-of-all-the-harm-done-by-hollande-to-muslims/|script-title=en:‘This Is Because of all the Harm Done by Hollande to Muslims’|work=The New York Times|date=2015-11-13|accessdate=2015-11-13|language=en|archive-date=2015-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115081859/http://www.nytimes.com/live/paris-attacks-live-updates/this-is-because-of-all-the-harm-done-by-hollande-to-muslims/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995227/Paris-shooting-Many-feared-dead-live.html|title=Paris shooting: Scores killed and injured after 'Kalashnikov and grenade attacks' across French capital with dozens of hostages taken - Further suggested links to Syria|quote="I clearly heard them say 'It's the fault of (French President Francois) Hollande, it's the fault of your president, he should not have intervened in Syria'. They also spoke about Iraq," said Pierre Janaszak|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|accessdate=2015-11-13|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113212158/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995227/Paris-shooting-Many-feared-dead-live.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方表示會有更進一步的攻擊，急救人員也在劇院內部發生槍擊後趕到現場<ref>{{cite web |title=Paris shooting: Several killed and injured after 'Kalashnikov and grenade attacks' across French capital |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995227/Paris-shooting-Many-feared-dead-live.html |website=Telegraph.co.uk |accessdate=2015-11-13 |archive-date=2015-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113212158/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11995227/Paris-shooting-Many-feared-dead-live.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據現場的一名警員表示，其中一名攻擊者持有炸藥<ref name="BBCNewsLive">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-europe-34815972 |title=Paris attacks |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-date=2015-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115100301/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-europe-34815972 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

約在00:15時，警方展開攻堅<ref name=Nossiter/>。這波行動持續到了00:58便結束<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualites/2015/11/13/01001-20151113LIVWWW00406-fusillade-paris-explosions-stade-de-france.php |title=Attaques terroristes à Paris: des dizaines de morts, l'état d'urgence décrété |work=[[费加罗报|Le Figaro]] |quote=Selon plusieurs sources concordantes, l'assaut est terminé au Bataclan. Selon BFM-TV, deux terroristes auraient été tués. |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414081610/http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualites/2015/11/13/01001-20151113LIVWWW00406-fusillade-paris-explosions-stade-de-france.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方初步報告表示，估計劇院內約有100名民眾被殺害<ref name="BBCNewsLive"/><ref name="Haaretz story">[http://www.haaretz.com/world-news/1.685943 At Least 120 Deaths in Multiple Paris Terror Attacks] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/world-news/1.685943 |date=20151114051652 }}, Haaretz Daily, 14 Nov 2015</ref>；不過，隨後下修至87名<ref name=GuardNov15/>。最終，四名攻擊者死亡，其中三位引爆身上的炸彈自殺<ref name="BBCNewsLive" /><ref name=Nossiter/><ref name="AFP summary" />。第四位則被警察射中而引爆身亡<ref name="AFP summary" />。周圍的社區在這起事件後被封鎖<ref>{{cite web|first=Emily|last=Shapiro|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/100-dead-explosions-shootings-hostage-situation-paris/story?id=35186222|title=Paris Attacks: At Least 120 Dead After 'Terrorists' Stage Multiple Attacks and Take Hostages|work=ABC News|date=2015-11-13|accessdate=2015-11-13|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114090412/http://abcnews.go.com/International/100-dead-explosions-shootings-hostage-situation-paris/story?id=35186222|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

