web | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/paris-shooting-attacks-explosion-1.3318444 | title=Paris attacks: France shutting borders after deadly attacks, hostage taking | publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] | date=2015-11-13 | accessdate=2015-11-13 | archive-date=2015-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113235435/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/paris-shooting-attacks-explosion-1.3318444 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[法国政府|法国政府]]宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，这是自[[阿尔及利亚战争|阿尔及利亚战争]]以来法国首次宣布全境进入紧急状态<ref name="CBC News border, military, emergency"/>。巴黎实施了自1944年来的首次[[宵禁|宵禁]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zhgpl.com/doc/1040/0/4/2/104004270.html?coluid=70&kindid=1850&docid=104004270&mdate=1114100451 |title=法國71年以來首次宵禁　所有市民不得外出 |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117022716/http://www.zhgpl.com/doc/1040/0/4/2/104004270.html?coluid=70&kindid=1850&docid=104004270&mdate=1114100451 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

