stillepost.com/macau/article/166208-%e3%80%90%e5%b7%b4%e9%bb%8e%e6%81%90%e8%a5%b2%e3%80%91%e9%90%b5%e5%a1%94%e9%97%9c%e4%ba%86%e7%87%88%e7%86%84%e4%ba%86-%e5%90%84%e5%9c%8b%e8%97%8d%e7%99%bd%e7%b4%85%e5%93%80%e6%82%bc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

